    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"PrintaTicketLabel-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936425137/Creating+a+Repair+Ticket+video\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936425137\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Creating a Repair Ticket (video)</a> </p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936261245/Creating+a+Trade-In+Ticket+video\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936261245\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Creating a Trade-In Ticket (video)</a> </p></li></ul><p /><p /><p>You can print a ticket label for a Repair Ticket at any time from the &quot;Ticket View&quot; screen. This is the screen you see after saving a ticket, and after looking up a ticket.</p><p>Just click on the blue button with the QR code icon as pictured below.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-external-resource image-center\" src=\"https://i.embed.ly/1/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Flh5.googleusercontent.com%2F-EIDfXVbunio%2FUMuEAbZeY3I%2FAAAAAAAAAGI%2FfbRqGULnQ8A%2Fs1429%2Fprint-label.png&amp;key=afea23f29e5a4f63bd166897e3dc72df\" data-image-src=\"https://i.embed.ly/1/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Flh5.googleusercontent.com%2F-EIDfXVbunio%2FUMuEAbZeY3I%2FAAAAAAAAAGI%2FfbRqGULnQ8A%2Fs1429%2Fprint-label.png&amp;key=afea23f29e5a4f63bd166897e3dc72df\" loading=\"lazy\"></span>",
